And so we want to challenge
you to think about why that is.

00:07:41.617 --> 00:07:43.700
And maybe you could even
put your own explanations

00:07:43.700 --> 00:07:46.700
in our little message board,
on either YouTube or our page,

00:07:46.700 --> 00:07:47.600
if you're curious.

